ArtyTorrent Pack 60-Ueberschall House Essentials Instruments-WAV
----------------------------------------------------------------

Part 4 of the full Ueberschall House Essentials sample disc. This pack is full of oneshot instrument samples mostly with A as the root note, but some multisamples are also included, so fire up your sampler and get key-mapping!

Torrent contains 13 RAR files with 399 oneshot samples
------------------------------------------------------
Categories are:
Rhodes, Piano, Organ, Chord, Lead Synth, Saw Lead, Strings, Pad, Brass, Stabs.

All samples are normalized 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz.

More House Essentials later today.

Comments/thanks/requests are welcome.
